<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALLA BREVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN HENKEN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Schubert: Sonatas, D. 821, 384, &amp; 408; Rondo, D. 895.Joseph Swensen, 
violin; Jeffrey Kahane, piano. RCA 7962-2-RC (compact disc). These performances 
are emotionally direct and remarkably sweet, yet without any hint of cloying 
sentimentality. The feeling is unaffected, the techniques sure and evenly 
yoked, and the results easily hold the ear. JOHN HENKEN 
</P>
