<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE FACTS ABOUT VEAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am disturbed that someone might believe Sandi Bouchard's ludicrously 
inaccurate letter (Sept. 3), which condemns Calendar and others for airing 
views about the condemnable (albeit legal) practices connected with formula-fed 
confined veal calves. 
</P>
<P>
White veal is an unnatural product obtained by unnatural means. Its production 
should be outlawed in this country as it has been in Sweden and some other 
countries. These nations are banning facts, not fictions. 
</P>
<P>
GENE BURKE 
</P>
<P>
Woodland Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
