<DOCID> 108342 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 17, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Real Estate; Part 8; Page 4; Column 1; Real Estate Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
