<HEADLINE>
<P>
CONQUERING HERO WINS FEATURE RACE AT FAIRPLEX PARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Conquering Hero held off Stylish Winner for a half-length victory in the 
$53,900 Phil D. Shepherd Stakes Saturday at Fairplex Park. 
</P>
<P>
Conquering Hero, with Martin Pedroza aboard, completed the 1 1/16 miles in a 
stakes-record 1:42 3/5 and earned $31,400 to move past $450,000 lifetime. 
</P>
<P>
Conquering Hero paid $17.80, $7.80 and $5.20. Stylish Winner, a runner-up in 
the Shepherd last year, paid $4.60 and $3. Alandvon was third and returned 
$12.00. 
</P>
</TEXT>
