<P>
Photo, Cal State Fullerton's Mike Pringle eludes Colorado State defender in 
Fort Collins, Colo. Saturday. Rams gave Earle Bruce his first Division I 
victory since he left Ohio State, 42-14. Associated Press 
</P>
