<HEADLINE>
<P>
BODY OF WOMAN FOUND IN RURAL AREA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The badly decomposed body of an adult woman was found Saturday along a rural 
portion of San Pasqual Road in the northeastern corner of San Diego, police 
said. 
</P>
<P>
Homicide detectives said the body was partially covered and lying on top of a 
drainage ditch. A coroner's autopsy is scheduled. 
</P>
<P>
Investigators are also checking to see whether the case is connected to a 
number of unsolved killings of prostitutes in the county during the past 
several years. 
</P>
<P>
Police from Escondido, whose city boundaries are near the area, were contacted 
first and later notified San Diego authorities. 
</P>
</TEXT>
