<P>
Recording Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091789-0128 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 108572 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 17, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
