doesn't discriminate against homosexuals. 
</P>
<P>
Among other tactics used by the Traditional Values Coalition: a 15-year-old 
cheerleader chanting bad AIDS jokes. Another picket sign read, "God Is Judge." 
If this is true, then who are they to appoint themselves as prosecutor 
(persecutor?) and jury? 
</P>
